<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ج- الملحق بمزيد الرُّباعيءّ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١- <span class="c2">(فَعَوْلَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(جَبَوْنَنٍ)</span> –اسم وادٍ- ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(فَعَوْلَلٍ)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(حَبَوكَرٍ)</span> وهو الدّاهية.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢- <span class="c2">(فُعْلُول)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(بُهْلُول)</span> ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(فُعْلُول)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(عُصْفُور)</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣- <span class="c2">(فُعْلال)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(قُرْطاطٍ)</span> وهو الدّاهية، وغيرها – ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(فُعْلالٍ)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(قُرْطَاسٍ)</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٤- <span class="c2">(فَعَلُول)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(حَلَكُوكٍ)</span> شديد السواد- ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(فَعَلُول)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(قَرَبُوسٍ)</span> .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٥- <span class="c2">(فِعْيَوْل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(عِذْيَوْطٍ)</span> وهو من يُحْدِثُ عند الجماع؛ ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(فِعْلَول)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(فِرْدَوْسٍ)</span> .<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٦- <span class="c2">(افْعَنلأَ)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(احْبَنْطَأَ)</span> ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(افْعَنْلَلَ)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(احْرَنْجَمَ)</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٧- <span class="c2">(افْعَنلَى)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(اسْلَنْقَى)</span> ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(افْعَنْلَلَ)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(احْرَنْجَمَ)</span> .<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٨- <span class="c2">(افْعَنلَل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(اقعَنسَسَ)</span> ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(افْعَنْلَلَ)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(احْرَنْجَمَ)</span> .<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٩- <span class="c2">(افْوَعَلَّ)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(اكْوَهَدَّ)</span> الفَرَخُ إذا ارتعدَ؛ ملحق بـ <span class="c2">(افْعَلَلَّ)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(اسْبَطَرَّ)</span> .<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١٠- <span class="c2">(أُفْعُول)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(أُمْلُودٍ)</span> وهو النّاعم؛ ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(فُعْلُولٍ)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(عُسْلُوجٍ)</span> وهو الغضُّ النَّاعم.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١١- <span class="c2">(إفْعِيل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(إِمْلِيدٍ)</span> وهو النَّاعم –أيضاً- ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(فِعْلِيلٍ)</span> كـ <span class="c2">(قِطْمِيرٍ)</span> .<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١٢- <span class="c2">(إفْعَوْل)</span> نحو <span class="c2">(إدْرَوْنٍ)</span> وهو أصل الشّيء، ألحق بـ <span class="c2">(فِعْلَولٍ)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>